{"id":"b44757ec-c05a-42ee-ac96-2383320cdcbb","name":"Raphael Chavez","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">✸ —<strong> KΑΣ </strong>— ✸<br><strong> </strong>oc | 2010's setting | childhood brat enemy</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_b4fb7b6f-d42c-431e-bdc4-2d1efcb0fd1e.webp?width=1000\"><em><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\">Oh, you two hate each other, so much from the moment you exchanged your first look, maybe when you were about five?</span></em></p><p><em><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\">Raphael is so full of himself and manipulative, but that's not why you hate each other, you just didn't hit off. And of course, you had to go to the same university besides being forced to basically grow up together because of your parents' friendship.</span></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)\">.</span></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 632px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_2c069dee-d376-4c12-ad64-ece47d7c7ae7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">'Another enemies to lovers, Chloe?'</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">YES</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">! You know I'm a sucker for it, and get ready for even more to come!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">I was racking my brains to create another frat boy, but finally, Raphael came to life.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">I hope you like it, I'm already cracking my knuckles getting ready to put <br>him in his place for saying he doesn't think I'm hot. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Who does he think he is?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 144px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_05f33f70-9663-4235-85b9-e4e6df0c44f8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 644px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_ee2e4e5b-4c2b-4b15-bd78-e6b51ac08eac.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">This is the </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">second</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> bot of the </span><strong>KΑΣ</strong>'s<strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">frat boys.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">Well, the name itself says all about the series. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">Frat, fresh, young, and dumb boys who don't think twice about breaking your heart </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">or maybe being the love of your life.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 641px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_67de19e3-6500-4a22-a291-4c4485862111.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/900718ac-3be5-4687-83b5-1bd628150cdf_character-tyee-singh\" rel=\"noo